Thank you Cloud 🤍 I trusted in you and you gave me your heart in every class we jumped as we climbed our way up the 5* classes to finish our tour jumping the QE II Cup. We set goals, worked hard, trusted in our team and our abilities, and achieved beyond expectations. Grateful for the invaluable experience gained jumping this summer tour at Spruce Meadows and looking forward to returning for the Masters 🙏🏼🏆

This month’s #RiderSpotlight is here 🤩 For this month’s spotlight, we caught up with Hannah Selleck, who is making quite the name for herself in the show jumping world. Just a few weeks ago, Hannah and Cloud 39 moved up to the 5* level at Spruce Meadows, finishing the circuit with a top-twelve placing in the ATCO Queen Elizabeth II Cup! 🏆

Tap the link in our story to read the full article!

This accomplishment stands out in an elite gathering of international riders. Witness this incredible competition on ClipMyHorse.TV! ▶️
